Yersinia * Linux 

# UseCase: 
[To perform DHCP Starvation Attack]

::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

$ yersina -I 
$ press any key, and then press h for help to view Available Commands
$ press q to exit
$ press F2 to select DHCP mode
$ press x to list available attack options
$ press 1 to start a DHCP starvation attack
$ To Stop press q 

::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
